headline: J&J Strikes Drug Pricing Deal With Trump, Gets Tariff Reprieve
summary: JNJ cuts U.S. drug prices under a Trump deal, gains a tariff reprieve, and accelerates a $55 billion push to expand domestic manufacturing.

headline: J&J cuts MFN deal with the Trump administration, bolsters US onshoring efforts
summary: The New Jersey pharma will now offer some of its branded medicines on the US government-created DTC platform, TrumpRx.gov.
